<br>
&gt; Or does it mean have your tongue in tht hard part <br>
&gt; then flick to the front of your mouth when you <br>
&gt; pronounce it?(using this method is the closest i <br>
&gt; have got to the sound like on the sound files <br>
&gt; they give you for &quot;ra&quot; etc.<br>
<br>
The above paragraph, quoted from your post, is correct.<br>
The tongue starts with its tip pressed against the roof of your mouth, about a finger's-width behind your top teeth.  Build up a little air pressure from your lungs, and then let your tongue relax so the air flicks your tongue forward.<br>
<br>
The result is a heck of alot like a D, but pronounced with your tongue further back in your mouth at the start, not pressed against your front teeth.<br>
<br>
Good luck with your studies.<br>
<br>
Oh... another hint:  &quot;FU&quot; in Japanese is NOT said like an English F-sound.  The English F-sound is made by holding back your breathe while your top teeth bite down on your bottom lip.<br>
In the Japanese version, there's no contact, and your teeth are not involved.  Instead, your lips come close together, and laod flat like a line, not curled like a kiss.  Your lips DO NOT TOUCH.  You say a &quot;HU&quot; sound with your lips almost closed, and push the air out in a rush, aaaalmost like an &quot;F&quot; sound. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm5.showPrevMessage?topicID=914.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm5.showNextMessage?topicID=914.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=914.topic&index=2><img src=http://www.polykarbon.com/bbsimage/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm5.emailToFriend?topicID=914.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm5.threadControl?topicID=914.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm5.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=914.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm5.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=914.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of 